# Project Rules

- This project is Rangers, a tmux-based agent orchestration platform.
- Preserve the config-driven launcher model centered on `rangers/rangers.conf`, `rangers/<role>.prompt`, and `rangers/constitution.prompt`.
- Keep swarm state project-local under `.rangers/`, worktrees under `.worktrees/`, and helper scripts under `rangertools/`.
- Prefer simple shell-based orchestration over adding heavier runtime infrastructure.
- Maintain clear role boundaries, reliable startup behavior, and explicit agent handoff mechanisms.
